# 先排除所有
*

# 只保留代码和文档
!*.py
!*.md
!docs/
!docs/**/*
!_board_deploy_package/
!_board_deploy_package/**/*
!_board_deploy_package_v17/
!_board_deploy_package_v17/**/*
!_board_deploy_package_v19/
!_board_deploy_package_v19/**/*
!from_pc/
!from_pc/**/*.py
!from_pc/**/*.md
!heatmap_verify/
!heatmap_verify/**/*.md
!.gitignore

# 排除缓存
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# 排除二进制模型文件（即使在白名单目录中也排除）
*.joblib
*.pkl
*.pth
*.npy
*.tar
*.zip

# 排除废弃目录
_废弃_污染数据与旧模型_待手动删除/
